data.name: ListEntryEvent
desc: specifies the event which is notified when a change in a string entry list occurred

items.name: Count
lines: denotes the number of changed entries, in case a change of an entry range is being notified.

items.name: Entries
lines: The concrete semantics of the value depends on the concrete event being notified.

items.name: Position
lines: denotes the position where a change occurred.
The concrete semantics of the value depends on the concrete event being notified.
